		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Risk assessment</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p><b>Risk assessment</b> is a step in a <a href="/wiki/Risk_management" title="Risk management">risk management</a> process. Risk <a href="/wiki/Assessment" title="Assessment">assessment</a> is the determination of <a href="/wiki/Quantitative" title="Quantitative">quantitative</a> or <a href="/wiki/Qualitative" title="Qualitative">qualitative</a> value of risk related to a concrete situation and a recognized <a href="/wiki/Threat" title="Threat">threat</a> (also called hazard). <i>Quantitative risk assessment</i> requires calculations of two components of <a href="/wiki/Risk" title="Risk">risk</a>: <i>R</i>, the magnitude of the potential loss <i>L</i>, and the probability <i>p</i> that the loss will occur.</p>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:364px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Risk.jpg" class="image" title="Risk"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d2/Risk.jpg" width="362" height="332" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Risk.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Risk</div>
</div>
</div>
